headline: GE Aerospace : U.S. Navy awards GE Aerospace Performance Based Logistics Contract for Avionics
summary: CINCINNATI - February 24, 2025 - GE Aerospace has been awarded a contract to provide performance-based logistics avionics support for the F/A-18, AV-8B and AH1-Z aircraft globally. ...
